name: reversalOfUnpostedVoucherMatch

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to 'Voucher Match' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Voucher Entries,Voucher Match}

testSteps.description: Then the 'Voucher Match' page and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Supplier' to '26158'
When i clear the business unit
When I click the 'Search' button
When I click the 'See More Details' button
When I click the checkbox of the first invoice row
When I click on 'Match' button
Then the 'Payment Information' and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Invouce Number' to 'RtNRXFevgG'
When I click on 'Continue' button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
When I click on 'Validate' button
When I click on 'Save' button

testSteps.description: Then the 'Voucher Match Successfully Created' modal should show up
When I click on 'Exit' button from modal
Given that I'm logged into 'Voucher Entry Review' page
Then the 'Voucher Entry Review' page and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Batch Number' using saved value
When I click on 'Search' button
Then the 'Review Voucher' search result should show up
When I select the first voucher entry
Then the view entries button of the first voucher entry should be enabled
Then the edit button of the first voucher entry should be enabled
When i click on delete button of the first voucher entry
Then the voucher review delete voucher modal should show up
When i click on modal confirm button
Then the voucher successfully deleted notification should show up
When I click on 'Search' button
Then the 'Review Voucher' search result should be empty

title: Reversal of unposted voucher match
